{"tid":1679322,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨義工申請","createTime":"2019-10-28T06:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T07:12:18.000Z","uid":137638,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9914dd4e1c0d919afb604afa2b268f765cbd4416","tid":1679322,"uid":137638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/THwrHk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTHwrHk6.jpg&h=6af23306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生歷量全力支持民主派參選人    <br />\n<br />\n區議會是香港地區層次的議會，就市民日常生活事務向政府提供意見。    <br />\n<br />\n學生歷量在此招募學生義工為各區民主派候選人助選。助選工作非常簡單，包括派傳單、叫口號、舉宣傳牌等。希望大家踴躍幫忙🙏🏻    <br />\n<br />\n義工申請表: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSen3iY07zRM37Co8C4EjywqaBBudgA7MWU48kRexeoQnH3gYw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSen3iY07zRM37Co8C4EjywqaBBudgA7MWU48kRexeoQnH3gYw%2Fviewform&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD56EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=d1c34ec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSen3iY07zRM37Co8C4EjywqaBBudgA7MWU48kRexeoQnH3gYw/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"087224c1472f4abb4f35b8f46a997e462b6c326f","tid":1679322,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"22aba60cccd196bcefe84dfd65a4caf3a3f24e9b","tid":1679322,"uid":137638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"幫手推推"},{"pid":"55179f78ea4386bac63c7636ab029aa32ee81d7a","tid":1679322,"uid":137638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8c8a8298900986b2560404e4cbb2383aee84299d","tid":1679322,"uid":137638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:5